{
  "texts": [
    "Site frequency spectrum was calculated using ANGSD 112 with the VCF file containing wild individuals and repetitive regions filtered out.",
    "The ancestral states were estimated as described above.",
    "For each of the models, 100 parameter files were simulated.",
    "For each parameter file, 1,000,000 simulations were run; monomorphic sites were not used.",
    "Maximum composite likelihood estimation of parameters was carried out with 40 expectation-conditional maximization iterations."
  ]
}